<!-- CHECKPOINT: must output Session End summary -->

6.1. Ensure all tests pass on both build paths
```
cmake --build build --config Debug 2>&1 | Select-Object -Last 20
ctest --test-dir build --output-on-failure 2>&1 | Select-Object -Last 30
```

6.2. Update `todo_list` with current status

6.3. Update `specs/phases/phase-{nn}-{id}.md` with progress checkpoint
     - Update current Task file: set `**Current Step**` and `**Resume Hint**`
       (e.g., `"Step 3: IFoo.h done, FooImpl.cpp in progress"`)

6.4. **Self-Audit** — compare workflow CHECKPOINTs executed in this session:

     | CHECKPOINT | Executed? | Notes |
     |---|-----|----|
     | Startup Summary (§1.7) | YES/NO | — |
     | Quality Gate (if planning) | YES/NO/N/A | — |
     | Gate Check (if phase complete) | YES/NO/N/A | — |
     | Anchor Audit (if 5+ Tasks done) | YES/NO/N/A | — |

     If any mandatory CHECKPOINT was skipped, explain why.

6.5. Provide brief summary:
     - What was completed (list Task IDs)
     - Current Task in progress (if any)
     - Blockers or decisions needed
     - Where to continue next session

